_sText:
This is new version of the de_kylpylasauna and have lots of improvements like: More detailing , Cubemaps and all bugs fixed. Also a whole new bombsite!.

TERRORISTS:
Try to blow up the whole place by planting a bomb in the sauna or the roof!

COUNTER-TERRORISTS:
Stop the evil terrorist for destroying the beautiful resort and the sauna!

BOMBSITES:
A on the both saunas.
B on the roof.

SPAWNPOINTS:
Map contains now 24 spawnpoints 12 Ct spawns and 12 terrorists spawns.

NOTE:
The recommended amount of players is up to 10.

I hope you enjoy this map and leave feedback :P
